@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

state StartRunning <<choice>>
state ConfigurationMode <<choice>>
state RunningState <<choice>>
state DataCollection <<choice>>
state SummaryPreparation <<choice>>
state StatusChecking <<choice>>
state ControlledMode <<choice>>
state ShutdownCondition <<choice>>

[*] --> StartRunning

state Restart
Restart : do / Power on system
Restart : exit / System ready to run

state EnterConfiguration
EnterConfiguration : entry / Requirement for changes or power-saving settings
EnterConfiguration : do / Enter configuration mode
EnterConfiguration : exit / Configuration mode active

state ReturnRunning
ReturnRunning : entry / Completed configuration
ReturnRunning : do / Return to running state
ReturnRunning : exit / Running state active

state CollectData
CollectData : entry / Triggered by clock while running
CollectData : do / Collect data
CollectData : exit / Data collected

state PrepareSummary
PrepareSummary : entry / Upon request
PrepareSummary : do / Prepare and send out weather summary
PrepareSummary : exit / Summary prepared

state CheckStatus
CheckStatus : entry / Upon request
CheckStatus : do / Check own status
CheckStatus : exit / Status checked

state ReturnControlledMode
ReturnControlledMode : entry / Through remote control
ReturnControlledMode : do / Move into controlled mode
ReturnControlledMode : exit / Controlled mode active

state Shutdown
Shutdown : entry / Given shutdown command while running
Shutdown : do / Return to shut down condition
Shutdown : exit / System shut down

StartRunning --> Restart
Restart --> EnterConfiguration
EnterConfiguration --> ConfigurationMode
ConfigurationMode --> ReturnRunning
ReturnRunning --> CollectData
CollectData --> PrepareSummary
PrepareSummary --> CheckStatus
CheckStatus --> RunningState
RunningState --> CollectData
ControlledMode --> [*]
Shutdown --> ShutdownCondition

@enduml
